,"commit_message":"* Match ftPp_SpecialAirHiStart_0_Anim\n\n(cherry picked from commit 9fb4561fa7c80cbe4fc3cb6eb40fa356f31cbf3f)\n(cherry picked from commit 6f564b22b258e69a2122cc88c8039a48d43099da)\n\n* Match ftCo_8009DB50\n\n(cherry picked from commit f84773019aca30536e1bd7659b3774a4fbede9d1)\n(cherry picked from commit f235ce14841f84233c7a6c9c13921d636b4bcba8)\n\n* Match ftCo_800D0EC8\n\n(cherry picked from commit 8bb8888aacb16eb92b18cab13781686018635eae)\n(cherry picked from commit 9b876bd7714a0a16ba5d670ad1e5663d1ab18d97)\n\n* Match grZebes_801D8558\n\n(cherry picked from commit fd9df6dcc3d1de94109924d82eea291af1f2dd5e)\n(cherry picked from commit 7a4c15cb0ca69d34b5246ba75c42fba0885d39c2)\n\n* Match grBigBlueRoute_8020B9D4\n\n(cherry picked from commit 66e87551fb79dbd2c179351c7a5be018800afc7c)\n(cherry picked from commit 3d0911a3958417c98cb9bb4cad1af9b2f87aaccf)\n\n* Match grPura_80211FD8\n\n(cherry picked from commit 606a8ff7070acc67136722dc746b6111e1203d9c)\n(cherry picked from commit ef9bceeed2b1a921a7a6993b832aa5a81675b9f3)\n\n* Match gm_8016A9E8\n\nSurgically extracted from origin commit 800e05964 onto upstream's\ngm_1601.c (no sibling WIP). Header signature in gm_1601.h updated to\nmatch the new body: int gm_8016A9E8(u8 arg0, s8 arg1).\n\n* Match ftKb_SpecialNPe_8010BF90\n\nSurgical extraction from origin commit de4dc1cb46e (Match\nftKb_SpecialNPe_8010BF90) — body now uses (Fighter*)gobj->user_data\ncasts and ftKb_Init_804D9570/9574 instead of literals.\n\nThe original commit also touched fn_8010CE5C in the same file, but\nfn_8010CE5C is a 99.94% near-miss (not byte-identical against the\nprebuilt .o). Reverted that to upstream's stub so this PR contains\nonly the verified-100% changes.\n\n* grzebes: drop static keyword on forward decls\n\nThe four forward declarations for grZebes_801D9F30/9F84/9100/925C were\n`static` while their definitions later in the file are non-static.\nupstream's check-issues docker image flags this as a Semantic Issue\n(redeclaration linkage mismatch). Removing `static` aligns the\nforward decls with the definitions; no impact on compiled .o\n(grZebes_801D8558 still verifies at 100%).\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: JelleJurre <76777936+jellejurre@users.noreply.github.com>"},"assignee":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"merged":true,"mergeable":null,"rebaseable":null,"mergeable_state":"unknown","merged_by":{"login":"jellejurre","id":76777936,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjc2Nzc3OTM2","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/76777936?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre","html_url":"https://github.com/jellejurre","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jellejurre/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"comments":1,"review_comments":0,"maintainer_can_modify":false,"commits":10,"additions":313,"deletions":39,"changed_files":9}